<p><span class="Arial13-Bold">Authorized users&rsquo; access and responsibilities</span></p>
<p>When you add authorized users to your account, you&rsquo;re responsible for the charges they make. An authorized user can:</p>
<p>&Yuml; Get account information</p>
<p>&Yuml; Request statement copies</p>
<p>&Yuml; Request replacement cards</p>
<p>Please be sure to tell the authorized user this account history will show on their credit report.</p>
<p><span class="Arial13-Bold">Some things to keep in mind about an Authorized User Plus</span></p>
<p>Following are some things to remember about adding an Authorized User Plus to your account:</p>
<p>&Yuml; The credit limit available to the authorized user is FF02_DollarAmtNoDec(1) .</p>
<p>&Yuml; Your account will be charged an additional annual fee of FF02_DollarAmtNoDec(2) .</p>
